posting_body: ['Ask us about our move-in specials!', 'Enjoy our cozy collection of luxury apartments in Oakland, happily tucked in our little pocket of Temescal.', 'We’re dedicated to bringing you a thoughtful and welcoming sanctuary wrapped in the vibrant surrounds of Temescal.', 'We may be small in numbers (43 total residences), but we’re big in what we bring to the table with our unique floor plan options.', 'That’s our promise, and we want you to hold us to it.', 'Contact us today and schedule a tour to learn more about our wonderful community!', '-On-Site Management', '-Great Natural Light with Large Floor to Ceiling Windows', '-Elevator Access', '-Modern Kitchens and Finishes', '-Stainless-Steel and Energy Efficient Appliance Package', '-Garage Parking Available', '-Modern Grey Cabinetry', '-Wood-Style Plank Flooring', "-Expansive 9' Ceilings", '-Oversize Rain Shower Heads', '-Easy Access to Public Parking and Hiking Trails', '-Contemporary LED Lighting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
